20pilot%20warned%20air%20traffic%20control%20about%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkey-answer-to-chinas-growing-surface-navy-is-american-submarines-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20navy%3C%2Fa%3E%20live-firing%20exercise%20off%20the%20Australian%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20were%20unaware%20of%20the%20exercise%20until%20a%20pilot%20raised%20the%20alarm%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Sharp%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Airservices%20Australia%2C%20the%20government%20agency%20responsible%20for%20air%20safety%2C%20gave%20evidence%20to%20a%20Senate%20hearing%20in%20Canberra%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20Virgin%20Australia%20aircraft%20that%20advised%20one%20of%20our%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20that%20a%20foreign%20warship%20was%20broadcasting%20that%20they%20were%20conducting%20live%20firing%20300%20nautical%20miles%20off%20our%20coast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETask%20Group%20107%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-growing-navy-conducts-first-dual-aircraft-carrier-drills-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%20Navy%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20operating%20off%20the%20New%20South%20Wales%20coast%20in%20the%20Tasman%20Sea%2C%20between%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20It%20consisted%20of%20a%20frigate%2C%20a%20cruiser%2C%20and%20a%20replenishment%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnaked-man-ran-through-plane-knocked-crew-member-police-say-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVirgin%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%20pilot%20heard%20one%20of%20the%20vessels%20broadcasting%20on%20the%20international%20guard%20frequency%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20said%20Peter%20Curran%2C%20Airservices%20Australia's%20deputy%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20hearing%20that%20the%20government%20agency%20then%20commenced%20a%20hazard%20alert%20t