ia%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20posters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FChampionsTrophy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23ChampionsTrophy%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5RthDQTYLO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5RthDQTYLO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Pawan%20Durani%20(%40PawanDurani)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPawanDurani%2Fstatus%2F1894096938087170289%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2024%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20taken%20note%20of%20a%20security%20breach%20that%20occurred%20when%20a%20spectator%20entered%20the%20field%20of%20play%20during%20the%20New%20Zealand-Bangladesh%20match%20in%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20at%20the%20Rawalpindi%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20players%20and%20officials%20remains%20the%20top%20priority%20of%20the%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20responsible%20organisation%2C%20we%20have%20engaged%20with%20local%20security%20agencies%2C%20who%20have%20committed%20to%20increasing%20security%20personnel%20around%20the%20field%20of%20play%20at%20all%20venues%20and%20strengthening%20access%20control%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20involved%20was%20arrested%20and%20presented%20before%20a%20court%20on%20Tuesday.%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20has%20been%20permanently%20banned%20from%20entering%20all%20cricket%20venues%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20such%20incidents%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20PCB%20is%20working%20closely%20with%20security%20agencies%20and%20venue%20authorities%20to%20review%20and%20reinforce%20security%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20talking%20point%20ahead%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20refused%20to%20allow%20Team%20India%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20tournament.%20A%20huge%20saga%20had%20followed%2C%20involving%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20and%20the%20other%20teams.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20India%20would%20play%20all%20its%20games%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue%20(Dubai).%20As%20such%2C%20even%20the%20India-Pakistan%20tie%20was%20played%20in%20Dubai%2C%20despite%20Pakistan%20being%20the%20official%20hosts%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20hosting%20of%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20has%20been%20under%20immense%20scrutiny%20even%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament.%20Not%20only%20is%20this%20the%20first%20time%20since%201996%20that%20Pakistan%20are%20hosting%20a%20major%20ICC%20event%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20also%20experienced%20significant%20delay%20in%20completing%20the%20renovation%20of%20the%20stadiums%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20pitch%2C%20Pakistan%20have%20already%20been%20knocked%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20despite%20still%20having%20a%20game%20remaining.%20They%20were%20beaten%20by%20India%20by%20six%20wickets%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20slamming%20his%2051st%20ODI%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20face%20Bangladesh%20in%20an%20inconsequential%20Group%20A%20game%20in%20Rawalpindi%20on%20February%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740488820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F9a9pr038_fan-detained-india-flag_625x300_25_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Ffan-in-pakistan-dragged-by-collar-for-carrying-india-flag-at-champions-trophy-2025-internet-abuzz-7792099%22%