ings%20involving%20the%20president%20and%20even%20been%20there%20during%20informal%20events.%20However%2C%20Elon's%20birthplace%20might%20pose%20a%20significant%20hurdle%20to%20his%20eligibility%20for%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErrol%20also%20drew%20parallels%20between%20Elon's%20potential%20political%20journey%20and%20that%20of%20Donald%20Trump.%20He%20noted%20that%20Trump's%20brash%20New%20York%20demeanor%20made%20it%20challenging%20for%20him%20to%20connect%20with%20ordinary%20voters%2C%20and%20Elon%20might%20face%20similar%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20concerns%20about%20Elon's%20political%20aspirations%2C%20Errol%20discussed%20his%20son's%20role%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency.%20Errol%20revealed%20that%20the%20department's%20investigation%20uncovered%20widespread%20inefficiencies%20and%20waste%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20drastic%20decision%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20entire%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20found%20that%20the%20rottenness%20was%20so%20enormous%20that%20the%20only%20solution%20was%20to%20completely%20close%20down%20the%20entire%20department%20immediately.%20The%20problem%20wasn't%20just%20bad%20employees%3B%20it%20was%20an%20entire%20system%20of%20waste%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20despite%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Elon's%20alleged%20Nazi%20salute%20at%20Trump's%20inauguration%20ceremony%2C%20Errol%20defended%20his%20son%2C%20attributing%20the%20misunderstanding%20to%20Elon's%20struggles%20with%20public%20speaking.%20%26quot%3BElon%20is%20a%20terrible%20public%20speaker.%20He%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20learn.%20We%20all%20do...Knowing%20him%20as%20well%20as%20I%20do%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20know%20him%20very%20well%2C%20that%20he%20was%20struggling%20to%20get%20through%20his%20little%20speech%20as%20fast%20as%20possible%20and%20to%20try%20and%20look%20as%20charming%20as%20possible%20as%20he%20could.%20But%20he's%20s