rgest%20producer%20of%20tactical%20and%20strategic%20drones%2C%20its%20defense%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20has%20ramped%20up%20its%20drone%20production%20since%20the%20start%20of%20Russia's%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20total%2C%20Ukraine%20delivered%20over%201.3%20million%20drones%20to%20soldiers%20in%202024%2C%20its%20commander%20in%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20become%20the%20world's%20largest%20producer%20of%20key%20military-use%20drones%2C%20the%20country's%20defense%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20become%20the%20biggest%20drone%20manufacturer%20in%20the%20world%2C%20drones%20of%20tactical%20and%20strategic%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20Rustem%20Umerov%20said%20during%20a%20Sunday%20press%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1i2fpoHZW5I%3Fsi%3DIh1fWHTSEhDovDn4%26t%3D3569%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econference%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Ukraine's%20%26quot%3BYear%202025%26quot%3B%20forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETactical%20drones%20support%20smaller-scale%20battlefield%20actions%2C%20often%20at%20close%20ranges%2C%20by%20gathering%20intelligence%20and%20supporting%20strikes%2C%20either%20as%20the%20munition%20or%20by%20providing%20targeting%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategic%20drones%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20often%20higher-end%2C%20high-altitude%20systems%20with%20the%20endurance%20to%20advance%20operations%20against%20higher-priority%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20same%20press%20conference%2C%20Oleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20Ukraine's%20commander%20in%20chief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1i2fpoHZW5I%3Fsi%3DrU_FUj3ZDEi8TWN5%26t%3D3951%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20country%20delivered%20over%201.3%20million%20drones%20to%20front-line%20soldiers%20in%202024.%20The%20general%20added%20that%20its%20long-range%20drones%20can%20strike%20targets%20up%20to%201%2C700%20kilometers%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6eB8fGCrz80%3Fsi%3DSff_xXSVZbnXqMYY%26t%3D3542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20his%20country%20produced%202.2%20million%20drones%20in%20total%20in%202024%20and%20planned%20to%20ramp%20up%20production%20further%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20defense%20ministry%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20Business%20Insider%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp-to-date%20and%20comprehensive%20data%20on%20various%20countries'%20respective%20drone%20production%20is%20scarce%2C%20making%20direct%20comparisons%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJune%202024%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Foutlook%2Fcmo%2Fconsumer-electronics%2Fdrones%2Fworldwide%3Fcurrency%3DUSD%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStatista%20Market%20Insights%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20data%20analysis%20service%20on%20market%20trends%2C%20said%20China%20was%20set%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20overall%20drone%20manufacturer%20in%202024%20and%20was%20on%20track%20to%20produce%202.9%20million%20drones.%20However%2C%20the%20data%20does%20not%20include%20drones%20for%20military%20purposes%2C%20though%20off-the-shelf%20drones%20for%20civilian%20use%20have%20been%20heavily%20repurposed%20for%20military%20use%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20further%20afield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fputin-says-drone-supplies-russian-army-increase-tenfold-2024-2024-09-19%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Russia%20was%20ramping%20up%20its%20own%20drone%20production%20to%20nearly%201.4%20million%20in%202024%2C%20a%20tenfold%20increase%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20are%20increasingly%20being%20used%20in%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%20for%20intelligence%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20bombing%20missions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-behind-80-russia-frontline-casualties-report-nyt-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprecision%20strikes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20military%20purposes%20by%20both%20state-level%20and%20non-state%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increased%20demand%20for%20counter-drone%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-has-drone-problem-heres-what-its-doing-about-it-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleased%20a%20new%20counter-drone%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20aimed%20at%20coordinating%20how%20different%20branches%20of%20the%20US%20military%20are%20responding%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20drones%20and%20making%20%26quot%3Bcountering%20unmanned%20systems%20a%20key%20element%20of%20our%20thinking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20been%20a%20hallmark%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20using%20the%20evolving%20technology%20to%20devastating%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20Ukrainian%20tactical%20drones%20face%20significant%20challenges%2C%20according%20to%20a%20February%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rusi.org%2Ftactical-developments-third-year-russo-ukrainian-war-february-2205.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20UK's%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%2C%20with%20a%2060-80%25%20failure%20rate%20in%20hitting%20targets%20%26quot%3Bdepending%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20front%20and%20the%20skill%20of%20the%20operators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20it%20said%20that%20they%20still%20account%20for%2060%20to%2070%25%20of%20damaged%20and%20destroyed%20Russian%20military%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20October%20speech%20to%20executives%20from%20dozens%20of%20foreign%20arms%20manuf