esident%20Donald%20Trump%20stated%20that%20his%20administration%20was%20considering%20a%20proposal%20where%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20savings%20from%20DOGE's%20cost-cutting%20measures%20would%20given%20to%20American%20citizens%2C%20while%20an%20equal%20amount%20will%20be%20used%20to%20pay%20down%20the%20federal%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20even%20under%20consideration%20a%20new%20concept%20where%20we%20give%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20DOGE%20savings%20to%20American%20citizens%2C%20and%2020%20per%20cent%20goes%20to%20paying%20down%20debt%20because%20the%20numbers%20are%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20it%20be%20implemented%2C%20cheques%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20could%20be%20sent%20per%20household%20after%20Musk-led%20DOGE%20wraps%20up%20its%20work%20in%20July%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'DOGE%20Dividend'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20called%20the%20'DOGE%20Dividend'%20was%20first%20developed%20by%20James%20Fishback%2C%20a%20DOGE%20supporter%20with%20connections%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20He%20took%20to%20X%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20share%20a%20four-page%20proposal%20which%20gained%20Musk's%20attention%2C%20who%20pitched%20the%20proposal%20to%20President%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20idea%20at%20the%20Miami%20event%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B%20love%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%2020%20per%20cent%20dividend%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20for%20the%20money%20that%20we're%20saving%20by%20going%20after%20the%20waste%2C%20fraud%20and%20abuse%20and%20all%20of%20the%20other%20things%20that%20are%20happening.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20great%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20this%2C%20Americans%20will%20tell%20us%20where%20there%20is%20waste.%20They'll%20be%20reporting%20it%20themselves.%20They%20participate%20in%20the%20process%20of%20saving%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20without%20providing%20any%20details%20about%20how%20such%20a%20plan%20could%20be%20implemented%20or%20what%20the%20remaining%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20DOGE%20savings%20would%20be%20used%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Would%20DOGE%20Dividend%20Work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFishback's%20much-talked-about%20plan%20hinges%20on%20the%20success%20of%20Musk-led%20DOGE's%20promise%20of%20slashing%20%242%20trillion%20in%20federal%20spending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20says%20that%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20DOGE's%20savings-around%20%24400%20billion%20be%20divided%20among%2079%20million%20tax-paying%20households%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20translates%20to%20a%20%245%2C000%20check%20per%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Could%20Get%20The%20Money%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20proposes%20that%20only%20people%20who%20pay%20more%20in%20federal%20income%20tax%20than%20they%20receive%20in%20government%20benefits%20would%20qualify%20for%20the%20DOGE%20dividends.%20Fishback%20argues%20that%20this%20design%20would%20prevent%20any%20inflationary%20spending%20and%20encourage%20financial%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20Americans%20don't%20pay%20such%20taxes%2C%20so%20they%20wouldn't%20get%20a%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DOGE%20Dividend%20is%20different%20from%20past%20stimulus%20checks%20because%20only%20tax-paying%20households%20receive%20it.%20There%20is%20nothing%20inflationary%20about%20paying%20off%20debt%2C%20saving%20for%20emergencies%2C%20or%20investing%20in%20college%20or%20retirement.%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740459420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F9pb9am3o_elon-musk_625x300_19_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famericans-to-get-part-of-doge-savings-this-amount-may-go-up-to-7788991%22%2C%22