%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20lives%20of%20underprivileged%20children%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidhi%E2%80%99s%20most%20impactful%20work%20has%20been%20her%20collaboration%20with%20NGOs%20like%20Global%20Concerns%20India%20and%20the%20Parinaam%20Foundation%20to%20bring%20the%20concept%20of%20creative%20writing%20to%20the%20children%20of%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20approached%20Global%20Concerns%20with%20my%20idea%2C%20they%20were%20welcoming%20and%20supportive%20of%20teaching%20the%20underprivileged%20children%20the%20art%20of%20creative%20writing%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Vidhi.%20Collaborating%20with%20NGOs%20was%20a%20conscious%20decision%20as%20Vidhi%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20as%20many%20children%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Vidhi%20was%20going%20in%20person%20to%20their%20community%20hall%20in%20LR%20Nagar%20and%20teaching%20the%20children%20in%20a%20tiny%2C%20dim-lighted%20room.%20But%20she%20realised%20the%20need%20for%20these%20children%20to%20have%20different%20experiences%20in%20life%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-45_11zon-1738839785-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vidhi%20conducting%20a%20workshop%20for%20kids%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-45_11zon-1738839785-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A