lding%20red%20pandas%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAligned%20with%20the%20Darjeeling%20Forest%20Division%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20habitat%20protection%2C%20the%20Padmaja%20Naidu%20Zoo%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20research%2C%20breeding%2C%20and%20rewilding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20focus%20is%20not%20merely%20on%20rewilding%2C%20but%20on%20rewilding%20robust%20and%20genetically%20diverse%20populations.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20meticulous%20studies%20are%20conducted%20on%20the%20health%20and%20genetic%20fitness%20of%20the%20red%20pandas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vishwanath%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20begin%20by%20carefully%20selecting%20individuals%20based%20on%20their%20pedigree%20and%20genetic%20diversity.%20Then%2C%20we%20implement%20a%20series%20of%20interventions%20to%20minimise%20the%20impact%20of%20human%20imprinting%2C%20ensuring%20they%20can%20adapt%20and%20survive%20in%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Holeyachi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_TAi0ESspY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC_TAi0ESspY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C