%20a%20Swiss%20army%20knife.%20You%20can%20do%20many%20things%20with%20it.%20If%20you%20have%20many%20tools%20in%20your%20genetic%20constitution%2C%20then%20you%20have%20a%20better%20ability%20to%20deal%20with%20diseases%2C%20anything%20that%20might%20happen%20to%20the%20population%20due%20to%20some%20infection%20and%20sudden%20climatic%20and%20natural%20disaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20where%20the%20zoo%E2%80%99s%20genetic%20biobank%20comes%20into%20play.%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20individuals%20we%20are%20releasing%2C%20proper%20genetic%20analysis%20is%20being%20done%20through%20scientific%20institutions%20like%20CCMB.%20We%20release%20individuals%20with%20high%20genetic%20diversity%20and%20heterozygosity.%20That%20contributes%20to%20the%20genetic%20makeup%20of%20the%20population%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Holeyachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenetic%20resources%20like%20DNA%2C%20RNA%2C%20sperms%2C%20oocytes%2C%20or%20any%20other%20bodily%20tissues%20are%20valuable%20and%20can%20be%20biobanked.%20Preserved%20in%20liquid%20nitrogen%20at%C2%A0%20-196%20deg%20C%2C%20they%20can%20remain%20alive%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Vasudevan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%20from%20LaCONES%20lab%2C%20CCMB%20conducted%20the%20training%20program%20for%20the%20officials%20%26amp%3B%20staffs%20of%20PNHZP%20%26amp%3B%20Bengal%20Safari%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSnapinst.app_451810555_7855430884543461_4770947284362880206_n_1080-1740104961-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthikeyan%20Vasudevan%2C%20Chief%20Scientist%20from%20LaCONES%20lab%2C%20CCMB%20conducted%20the%20training%20programme%20for%20the%20officials%20and%20staff%20of%20PNHZP%20%26amp%3B%20Bengal%20Safari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiobanking%20of%20endangered%20species%20is%20gaining%20popularity%20across%20the%20world%20as%20a%20promising%20conservation%20tool.%20Apart%20from%20providing%20invaluable%20information%20that%20could%20aid%20in%20understanding%20susceptibility%2C%20reproductive%20success%2C%20and%20adaptation%20to%20environmental%20change%2C%20biobank%20gametes%20(sperm%20and%20eggs)%20can%20be%20used%20for%20assisted%20reproductive%20technologies%20like%20artificial%20insemination%20or%20in%20vitro%20fertilisation%20(IVF).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTypically%20you%20can%20equate%20an%20endangered%20species%20to%20a%20person%20in%20an%20ICU.%20To%20help%20that%20person%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20give%20some%20support%2C%20put%20in%20some%20monitors%2C%20conduct%20tests%2C%20and%20check%2C%20and%20then%20give%20the%20possible%20best%20treatment%20so%20that%20that%20person%20recovers.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20with%20endangered%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Vasudevan%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20bringing%20it%2C%20making%20sure%20we%20provide%20everything%20to%20ensure%20it%20successfully%20increases%20in%20numbers%20and%20can%20be%20given%20a%20home%20in%20the%20wild%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaCONES%20also%20helps%20Darjeeling%20Zoo%20plan%20its%20conservation%20breeding%20programmes%20by%20screening%20animals%20for%20diseases%20and%20providing%20information%20on%20the%20founder%20populations%E2%80%99%20genetic%20makeup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20holistic%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20animals%20have%20a%20generation%20time%20%E2%80%94%20the%20period%20from%20birth%20to%20when%20they%20reach%20sexual%20maturity%20and%20produce%20their%20offspring.%20For%20red%20pandas%2C%20this%20is%2018-20%20months.%20But%20in%20the%20wild%2C%20numerous%20constraints%20impact%20this%20process%3A%20high%20mortality%20rates%20among%20the%20young%2C%20challenges%20in%20finding%20mates%2C%20potential%20food%20shortages%20after%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20predation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptive%20breeding%20programmes%20aim%20to%20mitigate%20these%20challenges%20by%20providing%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20adequate%20food%20and%20protection%20from%20predators%2C%20and%20by%20carefully%20selecting%20breeding%20pairs%20to%20maximise%20genetic%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FUntitled-design-6_11zon-1740105036.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darjeeling%20Zoo%20was%20shortlisted%20for%20the%20WAZA%20Conservation%20and%20Environmental%20Sustainability%20Awards%20in%202024%20for%20its%20red%20panda%20conservation%20efforts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F