%20Rupal%20focuses%20on%20sourcing%20fresh%20flowers%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20obstacle%20came%20when%20they%20faced%20a%20major%20setback%20with%20one%20of%20their%20vendors%20during%20the%20initial%20days.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20an%20issue%20with%20packaging%20where%20we%20placed%20an%20order%20with%20a%20vendor%20who%20messed%20up%20the%20production%20and%20then%20disappeared%2C%20refusing%20to%20pick%20up%20calls.%20For%20a%20small%20business%20just%20starting%2C%20this%20was%20a%20huge%20blow%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20real%20learning%20curve%20for%20us.%20We%20realised%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20have%20strict%20vendor%20contracts%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20this%20from%20happening%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270825%2Fyourdesicart-started-by-women-entrepreneurs-for-nri-shipping-from-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother-daughter%20duo%E2%80%99s%20deep%20bond%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shared%20vision%20have%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20business%E2%80%99s%20success.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20interfere%20with%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20work%2C%20and%20that%20gives%20us%20the%20space%20to%20grow%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rupal.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20my%20mother.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20creative%20I%20was.%20I%20always%20thought%20I%20was%20a%20science-oriented%20person%2C%20but%20I%20realised%20there%20is%20a%20creative%20side%20that%20should%20be%20explored%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20her%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20to%20the%20future%2C%20the%20entrepreneurs%20are%20focused%20on%20expanding%20Baked%20Bouquets%20beyond%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20grow%20slowly%2C%20but%20steadily.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20take%20our%20baked%20bouquets%20to%20different%20cities%20and%20let%20more%20people%20experien